{"tid":1649742,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一早叫左你地唔好呼籲人地帶口罩出街","createTime":"2019-10-12T18:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T06:54:36.000Z","uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fdbcbec99f3991ad772939de8aa29f132635b2a7","tid":1649742,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:18:09.000Z","msg":"一早叫左你地唔好呼籲人地帶口罩出街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1649521/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1649521/page/1</a><br />\n隔離POST, 唔係我作<br />\n帶口罩標籤自己, 結果班細路就出事<br />\n<br />\n一早話左帶口罩, 等同標籤自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1644771/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1644771/page/1</a><br />\n我之前已經講左<br />\n警告你地班撚樣, 唔好勇字行頭<br />\n你地來來去去都係果幾句, 出得黎就唔好驚, 要反抗<br />\n而家呢個係高風險, 極極極低效益既方法, 你地一味勇字行頭自HIGH, 仲小9唔同意既人<br />\n<br />\n而家細路比班魔警捉左, 我真係擔心佢地出事<br />\n一早叫左你地唔好呼籲人地帶口罩, 你地又唔撚聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52312180b38dffb40fdd302e91bfe4ae39b42711","tid":1649742,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"950afb515bb7e11f17f7c212415c91c132f970fe","tid":1649742,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:19:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9f6dbafb310d7a16223e62ed4c215defe11af26","tid":1649742,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:20:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n叫人帶口罩既做乜唔入黎"},{"pid":"bd828491040075c32900abe51e1c33464316b073","tid":1649742,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:22:45.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eee3e6e2f9c3ecf1427a7b439fbaeea3d9732320","tid":1649742,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:22:53